## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
1. Open the Admin Panel → Users view
2. Confirm 4 group cards appear (Approved, Pending, Organizers, Customers) with correct counts
3. Click each card → list expands, only one at a time
4. Each user row has working: Approve button, Role select, Details button
5. Use search/filter → cards update to match results
6. Open Subscriptions view → active services appear as dynamic groups on Users view
7. Resize window to mobile → cards stack, rows go vertical, no horizontal scroll

